    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "I don't think there is any reason not to allow a wider tooltip. \nMaybe with a min-width instead of a width (not sure what is used now). IIRC there might have been issues because of scrollbar, but we could re-test. The scrollbar might also explain  the 72 char behavior has most of us code on Macs+Chrome  where the scrollbar is invisible so we have a few more pixel to prevent wrap. \n\nWould like like to give it a shot in a PR ?\n"
